title: 16. How I'm Managing My Acne (Tess Solo Episode)
description: Hi friends, Tess here. In this episode I am discussing my journey with acne, how my struggle has given my career purpose, and what I am doing to minimize the condition (as well as what I'm NOT doing ) I hope it helps! Please let me know what you think and feel free to DM me if you have any questions or want to discuss this topic further! Xo  Tess' Instagram @myestytessa.dermaplus + Tess' YouTube: Tess Zolly Lauren's Instagram: @laurens.esthetics Music by LiQwYd --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/the-treatment-room/support
